    Based on gentoo-x86/net-irc/bip/files/bip-configure.patch
    See http://www.gnu.org/software/autoconf/manual/automake.html#User-Variables
    If user doesn't specify CFLAGS, default value is "-Wall -Wextra -g -O2".

